graph TD
A(home/main screen)-->B[/tap on plus icon next to your power points/]
B-->C[present 'add points' screen]
C-->D{'buy points' or 'play to win'}
D-->E[present 'choose purchase option' screen]
D-->F[present 'game' screen]
D-->M(cancel)
E-->G{choose amount of points}
G-->K(cancel)
G-->H{choose payment method}
H-->L(cancel)
H-->I[return success or failure of payment]
F-->J[return earned points]
